<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <title> URL Shortener Microservice </title>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0-alpha.6/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-rwoIResjU2yc3z8GV/NPeZWAv56rSmLldC3R/AZzGRnGxQQKnKkoFVhFQhNUwEyJ" crossorigin="anonymous">
    </head>
    <body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row mt-3">
            <div class="col-12">
                <h1> FreeCodeCamp API: URL Shortener Microservice </h1>
            </div>
        </div>
         <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="col-12">
                <h5> User stories: </h5>
                <ul class="list-group mt-4">
                    <li class="list-group-item"> I can pass a URL as a parameter and I will receive a shortened URL in the JSON response. </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item"> When I visit that shortened URL, it will redirect me to my original link. </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="row col-12 mb-2">
                <h3> Example creation usage: </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="row col-12 mb-3">
                <code> https://mahmoud-url-shortener.herokuapp.com/api/new/https://www.google.com </code>
            </div>
            <div class="row col-12 ">
                <code> https://mahmoud-url-shortener.herokuapp.com/api/new/https://www.facebook.com </code>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="row col-12 mb-2">
                <h3> Example creation output </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="row col-12 mb-3">
                <code> { "original_url":"http://www.facebook.com", "short_url":"https://mahmoud-url-shortener.herokuapp.com/rJA9JR-wb" } </code>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="row col-12 mb-2">
                <h3> Usage: </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="row col-12 mb-3">
                <code> https://mahmoud-url-shortener.herokuapp.com/rJA9JR-wb </code>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="row col-12 mb-2">
                <h3> Will redirect to: </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="row col-12 mb-3">
                <code> https://translate.google.com/ </code>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </body>
</html>